&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Once all villagers decided to pray for rain. &lt;br>
On the day of prayer, all the people gathered, &lt;br>
but only one boy came with an umbrella. &lt;br>
This is faith or innocence?&lt;/p>
&lt;p>When you throw babies in the air, &lt;br>
they laugh because they know you will catch them. &lt;br>
This is trust or helplessness or ignorance?&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>